window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>What happens when an Olympic athlete and a young divorcée start their new year together? One hot night, lots of laughter, and a little surprise.</b></p> <p>One night. That’s all I wanted: to start the new year on a good note and forget about the chaos last year brought.</p> <p>Enter Ryan. With his dark eyes, panty-melting smile, and sinful body, he’s the perfect distraction.</p> <p>When I’m left with more than just the spell-binding memories of our night together, I’m positively freaking out. Things get even more complicated when I find out how our lives are already intertwined.</p> <p>Will I be able to keep our connection a secret while we get to know each other, or will this whole mess blow up in my face?</p> <p><i>Secret Plunge </i>is a fun and sexy sports romance and the first book in the Kings of the Water series. All books in this series can be listened to as standalones.</p>"; 
